text.section:
Certified versions of the Kentucky Revised Statutes shall contain:
The Constitution of the United States;
The Constitution of this Commonwealth;
The text of all laws contained in the official version of the Kentucky Revised Statutes;
A full and accurate index of the statute laws and Constitution of this Commonwealth;
The rules of the Supreme Court of Kentucky, the Kentucky Rules of Civil Procedure, the Kentucky Rules of Criminal Procedure, and any other judicial materials specified by the Commission; and
Any annotations, historical notes, and other information that the Commission deems appropriate to include.
